How fast and accurate can you design? Are you ready to compete with students from around the world and win cool prizes?

Model Mania Student Prizes 20231081×292 56.6 KB

Model Mania Student Challenge 2023 starts now and the winner is announced at our global event 3DEXPERIENCE World 2023, February 12-15, 2023. 3DEXPERIENCE World is a hybrid event with in-person and virtual activities, Students can register for the virtual program for free that includes a chance at Model Mania, Certification Exams, and hundreds of breakout sessions from the best designers in the world that use SOLIDWORKS, xDesign and other technology by Dassault Systemes.

  1. Register for 3DEXPERIENCE World
  2. Sign up for Model Mania - read the rules and deadlines
  3. Get your free software
  4. Start designing!

More information can be found below,

Before kick off, there is still time to participate in the Model Mania Student Challenge 2023 Deadline Jan 27, 2023 and win prizes. Register for 3DEXPERIENCE World.

Last year’s winner is Nadir Oktay Kucukaltun, now interning at Tekyaz, our SOLIDWORKS reseller supporting Turkey’s Istanbul Regional.
